data.question: What is the source of the Face Detection code in ComfyUI-MuseTalk?
data.answer: The code for Face Detection in ComfyUI-MuseTalk has been taken from the [face_alignment](https://github.com/1adrianb/face-alignment) repository.

data.question: Has the Face Detection code been modified in ComfyUI-MuseTalk?
data.answer: Yes, the Face Detection code in ComfyUI-MuseTalk has been modified to take batches of faces at a time.

data.question: How has the Face Detection code from face_alignment been modified for ComfyUI-MuseTalk?
data.answer: The Face Detection code from the face_alignment repository has been modified to take batches of faces at a time for ComfyUI-MuseTalk.
